text: Dhal Al Misfir Cave Dhal Al Misfir is a cavern that is a natural landmark in the Rawdat Rasid area of Qatar.Dahl Al Misfir Cave Qatar TourismWhat caves are in Qatar? USAToday The cave contains fibrous gypsum crystals.Caves Qatar Digest Its depth is anywhere from 40 meters to at least 100 meters. The entrance is approximately 12 x 4.5 meters and its gypsum crystals derive from the Lower Dammam Formation and Rus Formation. ==See also== *Natural areas of Qatar ==References== Category:Landforms of Qatar Category:Caves of Qatar
